#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; is a program for viewing, extracting, creating and modifying archives. "
"&ark; can handle various archive formats such as <command>tar</command>, "
"<command>gzip</command>, <command>bzip2</command>, <command>zip</command>, "
"<command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</command>, <command>xz</command>, "
"<command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</command>, <command>deb</command>, "
"<command>xar</command> and <command>AppImage</command> (support for certain "
"archive formats depends on the appropriate command-line programs being "
"installed)."
msgstr ""
"<application>Ark</application> je program pregledanje, raspakivanje, "
"stvaranje i menjanje arhiva. Ume da rukuje raznim formatima arhiva, kao što "
"su tar, gzip, bzip2, ZIP, RAR, 7zip, XZ, RPM, CAB, DEB, XAR i AppImage (neki "
"od njih su podržani samo ako su instalirani odgovarajući programi komandne "
"linije)."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ark;'s main window"
msgstr "Glavni prozor <application>Arka</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to successfully use &ark;, you need KDE Frameworks 5. The library "
"libarchive version 3.1 or above is needed to handle most archive types, "
"including tar, compressed tar, rpm, deb and cab archives. To handle other "
"file formats, you need the appropriate command line programs, such as "
"<command>zipinfo</command>, <command>zip</command>, <command>unzip</"
"command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>unrar</command>, <command>7z</"
"command>, <command>lsar</command>, <command>unar</command> and "
"<command>lrzip</command>."
msgstr ""
"Za uspešno korišćenje <application>Arka</application>, trebaju vam Radni "
"okviri KDE‑a. Za rukovanje većinom vrsta arhiva — uključujući tar, RPM, DEB "
"i CAB — koristi se biblioteka libarchive izdanja 3.1 ili novijeg. Za "
"rukovanje ostalim formatima arhiva potrebni su odgovarajući programi "
"komandne linije, kao što su <command>zipinfo</command>, <command>zip</"
"command>, <command>unzip</command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>unrar</"
"command>, <command>7z</command>, <command>lsar</command>, <command>unar</"
"command> i <command>lrzip</command>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &ark;"
msgstr "Korišćenje <application>Arka</application>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening Archives"
msgstr "Otvaranje arhiva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open an archive in &ark;, choose <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>) from the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. You can also open archive files by dragging "
"and dropping from &dolphin;. Archive files should be associated with &ark;, "
"so you can also <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click a file in &dolphin; "
"and select <guimenuitem>Open with &ark;</guimenuitem> to open it or select "
"an extract action for this file."
msgstr ""
"Arhivu u <application>Arku</application> otvarate pomoću "
"<guimenuitem>Otvori...</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>) iz menija "
"<guimenu>Arhiva</guimenu>. Arhivske fajlove možete otvarati i prevlačenjem i "
"puštanjem iz <application>Dolphina</application>. Formati arhiva treba da su "
"pridruženi <application>Arku</application>, tako da možete kliknuti desnim "
"na fajl u <application>Dolphinu</application> i izabrati <guimenuitem>Otvori "
"pomoću Arkom</guimenuitem> da ga otvorite, ili izabrati jednu od radnji "
"raspakivanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have enabled the information panel in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"menu additional information about the selected folders or files in the "
"archive is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste u meniju <guimenu>Podešavanje</guimenu> aktivirali panel sa "
"podacima, videćete dopunske podatke o izabranim fasciklama i fajlovima u "
"arhivi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Operations"
msgstr "Postupci arhiviranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Various operations can be performed for an opened archive by using the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. For example, you can save the archive with "
"a different name using <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>. Archive "
"properties such as type, size and MD5 hash can be viewed using the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> item."
msgstr ""
"Nad otvorenom arhivom mogu da se izvrše razni postupci preko menija "
"<guimenu>Arhiva</guimenu>. Na primer, možete sačuvati arhivu pod drugim "
"imenom pomoću <guimenuitem>Sačuvaj kao...</guimenuitem>. Svojstva arhive, "
"poput tipa, veličine i MD5 disperzije, mogu se prikazati stavkom "
"<guimenuitem>Svojstva</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; has the ability to test archives for integrity. This functionality is "
"currently available for <command>zip</command>, <command>rar</command> and "
"<command>7z</command> archives. The test action can be found in the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"<application>Ark</application> može da ispituje integritet arhiva. Ova "
"funkcionalnost je trenutno dostupna za ZIP, RAR i 7zip arhive. Radnja "
"ispitivanja može se naći u meniju <guimenu>Arhiva</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Comments"
msgstr "Komentari u arhivi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; can handle comments embedded in <literal role=\"extension\">zip</"
"literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archives."
msgstr "Ark može da rukuje ugnežđenim komentarima u ZIP i RAR arhivama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Comments embedded in <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> archives are "
"automatically displayed."
msgstr "Komentari ugnežđeni u ZIP arhivama prikazuju se automatski."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archives you can modify a "
"comment with the actions <guimenuitem>Add Comment</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Edit comment</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Kod RAR arhiva, komentare možete uređivati radnjama <guimenuitem>Dodaj "
"komentar</guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem>Uredi komentar</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo>) u meniju <guimenu>Arhiva</guimenu>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing a comment"
msgstr "Uređivanje komentara."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The comment menu item is enabled only for <literal role=\"extension\">rar</"
"literal> archives."
msgstr "Stavka menija za komentare aktivna je samo za RAR arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a comment from a <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archive "
"delete the text in the comment window."
msgstr ""
"Komentar uklanjate iz RAR arhive tako što obrišete tekst u prozoru komentara."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Files"
msgstr "Rad sa fajlovima"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once an archive has been opened, you can perform various operations on the "
"files inside the archive. By selecting a file and using the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu, you can choose different operations to perform:"
msgstr ""
"Pošto otvorite arhivu, možete vršiti razne radnje nad fajlovima unutar nje. "
"Odabirom fajla i korišćenjem menija <guimenu>Fajl</guimenu>, možete izvršiti "
"neki od narednih postupaka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>) will open the file with &ark;'s internal "
"viewer. This is a fast read-only viewer, but does not support all file types."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Prikaži</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</"
"keycap><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>) otvara fajl u <application>Arkovom</"
"application> unutrašnjem prikazivaču. Ovo je brzi prikazivač, samo za "
"čitanje, ali ne podržava sve tipove fajlova."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem> will open the file in the associated "
"application for that file type."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Otvori</guimenuitem> otvara fajl u programu pridruženom tom "
"tipu fajla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Open With...</guimenuitem> allows you to choose which "
"application to open the file with."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Otvori pomoću...</guimenuitem> daje vam da izaberete kojim "
"programom otvoriti fajl."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Rename</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) This action allows to change names of both "
"files and folders. As in the Dolphin file manager, this action can be called "
"via a shortcut and renaming is done via inline editing. There are also "
"filename checks provided, which prevent usage of invalid characters such as "
"<userinput>/</userinput>, <userinput>.</userinput> and <userinput>..</"
"userinput> in filenames."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Preimenuj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) omogućava menjanje "
"imena fajlova i fascikli. Kao i u menadžeru fajlova <application>Dolphinu</"
"application>, ova radnja može da se pozove prečicom i preimenovanje se "
"obavlja utkanim uređivanjem. Prisutne su i provere imena fajla koje "
"sprečavaju upotrebu loših znakova, poput <userinput>/</userinput>, "
"<userinput>.</userinput> i <userinput>..</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> (<keycap>Del</keycap>) will remove the "
"currently selected file(s) from the archive. Note that this action is "
"undoable."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Obriši</guimenuitem> (<keycap>Del</keycap>) uklanja trenutno "
"izabrane fajlove iz arhive. Imajte na umu da se ova radnja ne može opozvati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) opens a submenu with previously accessed "
"folders, and you can choose to quickly extract into any of these or browse "
"to a non-listed folder. See the next section for more details on extraction."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Raspakuj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) otvara podmeni sa "
"prethodno posećenim fasciklama, odakle možete brzo izabrati neku u koju ćete "
"raspakovati, ili pregledati za nekom drugom fasciklom. Pogledajte naredni "
"odeljak za više detalja o raspakivanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</"
"keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo>): As in typical file managers, moving, pasting and copying are "
"provided. Users can move or copy files from different folders (which are "
"expandable in the tree view) and paste them to the same destination at once. "
"A folder can be copied into itself, but can not be moved. There are also "
"checks for conflicting filenames: You won't be able to copy or move files "
"into a folder that has entries with the same names - that could lead to data "
"loss."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Iseci</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</"
"keycap><keycap>X</keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Nalepi</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>): kao i u tipičnim "
"menadžerima fajlova, stavke se mogu premeštati, nalepljivati i isecati. "
"Korisnik može da premesti ili kopira fajlove iz različitih fascikli (koje su "
"proširive u prikazu stabla) i nalepi ih u isto odredište odjednom. Fascikla "
"može da se kopira na samu sebe, ali ne može da se premesti. Tu su i provere "
"sukoba u imenima fajlova: ne možete da kopirate fajlove u fasciklu koja već "
"ima istoimene stavke, kako bi se sprečio gubitak podataka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Add Files</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>) This action can be used to add files at any "
"location within the archive. If you select a folder and use this action, "
"files will be added to the selected folder. Otherwise, the new files will be "
"added to the root of the archive."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Dodavanje fajlova</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>) je radnja za dodavanje "
"fajlova na bilo koju lokaciju unutar arhive. Ako izaberete fasciklu pa "
"upotrebite ovu radnju, fajlovi će biti dodati u izabranu fasciklu. Inače će "
"biti dodati u koren arhive."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Files"
msgstr "Uređivanje fajlova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you edit and save a file which you opened using <guimenuitem>Open</"
"guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Open With...</guimenuitem>, Ark will ask you if "
"you want to update the file in the archive. If you answer Yes, the archive "
"will be updated with the saved file."
msgstr ""
"Ako uredite i sačuvate fajl koji ste otvorili pomoću <guimenuitem>Otvori</"
"guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Otvori pomoću...</guimenuitem>, "
"<application>Ark</application> će vas pitati želite li da ažurirate fajl u "
"arhivi. Ako odgovorite potvrdno, arhiva će biti dopunjena sačuvanim fajlom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extracting Files"
msgstr "Raspakivanje fajlova"

# >! ui: Action --> Actions
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once an archive has been opened in &ark;, it can be extracted. This can be "
"done by selecting <guisubmenu>Extract</guisubmenu> from the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu. This opens a submenu with previously accessed folders, and "
"you can choose to quickly extract into any of these. Alternatively, select "
"the submenu item <guisubmenu>Extract To...</guisubmenu> to open the "
"<guilabel>Extract</guilabel> dialog, where you can set various options that "
"affect the extraction. See below for information on the available options in "
"the Extract dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pošto se otvori u <application>Arku</application>, arhiva se može "
"raspakovati. To možete učiniti izborom <guisubmenu>Raspakuj</guisubmenu> iz "
"menija <guimenu>Fajl</guimenu>. Ovo otvara podmeni sa prethodno posećivanim "
"fasciklama, tako da možete izabrati brzo raspakivanje u jednu od njih. "
"Alternativno, izaberite stavku <guisubmenu>Raspakuj u...</guisubmenu> da "
"biste otvorili dijalog za raspakivanje, gde možete zadati razne opcije u "
"vezi sa raspakivanjem. Pogledajte u nastavku opise raspoloživih opcija u "
"ovom dijalogu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guibutton>Extract</guibutton> button in the toolbar to "
"access the same extraction options."
msgstr ""
"Za pristup istim opcijama raspakivanja takođe možete upotrebiti dugme "
"<guibutton>Raspakuj</guibutton> na traci alatki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To extract the entire archive, you can select <guisubmenu>Extract All</"
"guisubmenu> from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. This action "
"unconditionally extracts all files in the archive."
msgstr ""
"Celu arhivu možete da raspakujete tako što izaberete <guisubmenu>Raspakuj "
"sve</guisubmenu> iz menija <guimenu>Arhiva</guimenu>. Ova radnja bezuslovno "
"raspakuje sve fajlove iz arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to extract files and folders by simply dragging them with the "
"mouse to a folder in &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Fajlove i fascikle je moguće raspakovati prostim prevlačenjem mišem u "
"fasciklu u <application>Dolphinu</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: Extracting files from an archive does not change the archive and its "
"contents."
msgstr ""
"Napomena: raspakivanje fajlova iz arhive ne unosi izmene u njenom sadržaju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Extract dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog raspakivanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Extract</guilabel> dialog allows you to choose where the files "
"will be extracted to. The default location is the folder the archive is in. "
"The dialog can also be opened by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Dijalog raspakivanja vam omogućava da izaberete gde će fajlovi biti "
"raspakovani. Podrazumevana lokacija je fascikla u kojoj se nalazi sama "
"arhiva. Dijalog takođe možete otvoriti pritiskom <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ark;'s Extract dialog"
msgstr "<application>Arkov</application> dijalog raspakivanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can specify to extract the files into a subfolder. The default name of "
"this subfolder is the archive name without the filename extension, but you "
"can edit it to your needs. If you want to preserve paths when extracting, "
"select the <guilabel>Preserve paths when extracting</guilabel> option. You "
"may also choose to open the destination folder in &dolphin; or close &ark; "
"once the extraction is complete."
msgstr ""
"Možete zadati raspakivanje fajlova u novu potfasciklu. Podrazumevano ime "
"potfascikle biće ime arhive bez nastavka iz imena fajla. Ako želite da se "
"putanje očuvaju pri raspakivanju, uključite opciju <guilabel>Očuvaj putanje "
"pri raspakivanju</guilabel>. Takođe možete izabrati da se po završetku "
"raspakivanja otvori ciljna fascikla u <application>Dolphinu</application>, i "
"da se <application>Ark</application> zatvori."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If one or more files in the archive list are highlighted, you can also "
"select which files to extract:"
msgstr ""
"Ako je na spisku arhive istaknut jedan ili više fajlova, takođe možete da "
"izaberete šta treba raspakovati:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Selected files only</guilabel> extracts only the files which have "
"been selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samo izabrani fajlovi</guilabel> raspakuje samo izabrane fajlove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>All files</guilabel> extracts the entire contents of the archive."
msgstr "<guilabel>Svi fajlovi</guilabel> raspakuje celokupan sadržaj arhive."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating Archives and Adding Files"
msgstr "Stvaranje arhiva i dodavanje fajlova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new archive in &ark;, choose <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) from the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Novu arhivu u <application>Arku</application> stvarate izborom "
"<guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</"
"keycap><keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) iz menija <guimenu>Arhiva</guimenu>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create an archive"
msgstr "Stvaranje arhive."

# rewrite-msgid: /filename extension/extension/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then type the name of the archive, with the appropriate extension "
"(<literal role=\"extension\">tar.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">zip</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal>, &etc;) or select "
"a supported format in the <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> combo box and check "
"the <guilabel>Automatically add <replaceable>filename extension</"
"replaceable></guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Zatim možete upisati ime arhive, s odgovarajućim nastavkom (<literal role="
"\"extension\">tar.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, "
"<literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal>, itd.), ili izabrati jedan od "
"podržanih formata sa spiska <guilabel>Filter:</guilabel> i popuniti kućicu "
"<guilabel>Automatski dodaj .<replaceable>nastavak</replaceable></guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add files or folders to the new archive, choose <guimenuitem>Add Files..."
"</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
" Za dodavanje fajlova ili fascikli u novu arhivu, idite na "
"<guimenuitem>Dodaj fajlove...</guimenuitem> u meniju <guimenu>Arhiva</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An alternative way to add files to an archive is to drag one or more files "
"from e.g. &dolphin; into the main &ark; window, and it will be added to the "
"current archive. Note that files added in this way will always be added to "
"the root directory of the archive."
msgstr ""
"Drugi način za dodavanje fajlova u arhivu jeste prevlačenjem jednog ili više "
"fajlova, npr. iz <application>Dolphina</application>, u glavni prozor "
"<application>Arka</application>, što će ih dodati u tekuću arhivu. Imajte na "
"umu da će ovako dodati fajlovi uvek biti smešteni u korenu fasciklu arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional options are presented in collapsible groups at the bottom of the "
"dialog."
msgstr "Dodatne opcije su date proširivim grupama u dnu dijaloga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compression"
msgstr "Kompresovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A higher value generates smaller archives, but results in longer compression "
"and decompression times. The default compression level proposed by &ark; is "
"usually a good compromise between size and (de)compression speed. For most "
"formats the minimum compression level is equivalent to just storing the "
"files, &ie; applying no compression."
msgstr ""
"Veća vrednost rezultuje manjim arhivama, ali dužim vremenom kompresovanja i "
"raspakivanja. Podrazumevani stepen kompresije koji <application>Ark</"
"application> daje obično je dobar kompromis između veličine i brzine "
"kompresovanja. Kod većine formata najmanji stepen kompresije označava prosto "
"skladištenje fajlova, tj. bez ikakvog kompresovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">7z</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> archives you "
"can select between different compression methods."
msgstr ""
"Za RAR, 7zip i ZIP arhive možete da izaberete različite metode kompresije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that using compression methods other than the pre-selected defaults may "
"limit compatibility with file archivers. For example, opening <literal role="
"\"extension\">zip</literal> archives with compression methods other than "
"<quote>Deflate</quote> requires newer archiving software."
msgstr ""
"Imajte na umu da metodi kompresije različiti od podrazumevano izabranih mogu "
"smanjiti saglasnost sa drugim arhivarima fajlova. Na primer, da bi se "
"otvorila ZIP arhiva sa metodom kompresije različitim od deflatea neophodan "
"je noviji softver za arhiviranje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Password Protection"
msgstr "Zaštita lozinkom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you create a <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</literal> and "
"<literal role=\"extension\">jar</literal> archive you can protect it with a "
"password. Currently, only the <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> "
"format supports multiple encryption methods. For other formats that support "
"only one encryption method, the method is shown in the drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Kad pravite ZIP, RAR, JAR ili 7zip arhivu, možete je zaštititi lozinkom. "
"Trenutno, jedino format ZIP podržava više metoda šifrovanja. Za formate koji "
"podržavaju samo jedan metod, taj metod je prikazan u padajućem spisku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other encryption methods than the default <guilabel>ZipCrypto</guilabel> "
"might not be supported by all file archivers."
msgstr ""
"Metodi šifrovanja različiti od podrazumevanog ZipCrypto mogu ne biti "
"podržani u nekim arhivarima fajlova."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a password protected archive"
msgstr "Stvaranje arhive zaštićene lozinkom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose whether to require the password before showing the list of files. "
"This is called header encryption and is available only with the <literal "
"role=\"extension\">rar</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</"
"literal> formats. Header encryption is enabled by default (when available), "
"in order to offer the maximum protection for novice users."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite da li tražiti lozinku i za prikazivanje spiska fajlova. Ovo se "
"naziva šifrovanjem zaglavlja, i moguće je samo u formatima RAR i 7zip. "
"Podrazumevano je uključeno (ako je dostupno), da bi se novim korisnicima "
"pružila najveća zaštita."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multi-volume Archive"
msgstr "Višedelna arhiva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">rar</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal> formats you "
"can create multi-volume archives, also known as multi-part or split archives."
msgstr ""
"Kod formata ZIP, RAR i 7zip možete praviti višedelne arhive, takođe poznate "
"i kao podeljene arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A multi-volume archive is one big compressed archive split into several "
"files. This feature is useful if the maximum file size is limited, &eg; by "
"the capacity of a storage medium or the maximal size of an email with "
"attachments."
msgstr ""
"Višedelna arhiva je jedna velika kompresovana arhiva podeljena u nekoliko "
"fajlova. Ova mogućnost dobro dođe kada je veličina fajla ograničena, npr. "
"prostorom skladišnog medijuma ili najvećom veličinom poruke e‑pošte sa "
"prilozima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a multi-volume archive, check the <guilabel>Create multi-volume "
"archive</guilabel> checkbox and set a maximum <guilabel>Volume size</"
"guilabel> in the dialog. Then add all files to the archive and &ark; will "
"automatically generate the required number of archive volumes. Depending on "
"the selected format the files have an extension with consecutively numbering "
"scheme &eg; <filename>xxx.7z.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.7z.002</filename> "
"or <filename>xxx.zip.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.zip.002</filename> or "
"<filename>xxx.part1.rar</filename>, <filename>xxx.part2.rar</filename> &etc;."
msgstr ""
"Da napravite višedelnu arhivu, popunite kućicu <guilabel>Napravi višedelnu "
"arhivu</guilabel> i zadajte <guilabel>Veličina delova:</guilabel> u "
"dijalogu. Zatim dodajte sve fajlove u arhivu, i <application>Ark</"
"application> će automatski napraviti odgovarajući broj delova arhive. U "
"zavisnosti od izabranog formata, fajlovi će imati nastavke sa nekom šemom "
"uzastopnog numerisanja, npr. <filename>xxx.7z.001</filename>, "
"<filename>xxx.7z.002</filename> ili <filename>xxx.zip.001</filename>, "
"<filename>xxx.zip.002</filename> ili <filename>xxx.part1.rar</filename>, "
"<filename>xxx.part2.rar</filename>, itd."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To extract a multi-volume archive, put all archive files into one folder and "
"open the file with the lowest extension number in &ark; and all other parts "
"of the split archive will be opened automatically."
msgstr ""
"Za raspakivanje višedelne arhive, stavite sve njene fajlove u istu fasciklu "
"i otvorite <application>Arkom</application> fajl sa najmanjim brojem u "
"nastavku. Tada će biti automatski otvoreni i svi ostali delovi podeljene "
"arhive."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:386
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Using &ark; in the Filemanager"
msgid "Using &ark; in the File Manager"
msgstr "Upotreba <application>Ark</application> u menadžeru fajlova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking with the &RMB; on an archive in a filemanager like &dolphin; "
#| "displays a context menu with an item <guimenuitem>Open with Ark</"
#| "guimenuitem>. The menu has these additional items to extract an archive "
#| "using &ark;:"
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on an archive in a file manager like &dolphin; "
"displays a context menu with an item <guimenuitem>Extract</guimenuitem>. The "
"menu has these additional items to extract an archive using &ark;:"
msgstr ""
"Klik desnim dugmetom miša na arhivu u menadžeru fajlova, poput "
"<application>Dolphina</application>, daje kontekstni meni sa stavkom "
"<guimenuitem>Otvori pomoću Arkom</guimenuitem>. Meni sadrži još i sledeće "
"stavke za raspakivanje arhive <application>Arkom</application>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>Extract Archive Here, Autodetect Subfolder</guimenuitem> "
#| "creates a subfolder in the folder with the archive and extracts the "
#| "folders and files into it."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract here</guimenuitem> creates a subfolder in the folder "
"with the archive and extracts the folders and files into it. In case the "
"archive contains only one file or folder, no subfolder will be created."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Raspakuj arhivu ovde, pogodi potfasciklu</guimenuitem> stvara "
"potfasciklu u fascikli u kojoj je arhiva, i u nju raspakuje fascikle i "
"fajlove iz arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>Extract Archive Here, Autodetect Subfolder</guimenuitem> "
#| "creates a subfolder in the folder with the archive and extracts the "
#| "folders and files into it."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract here and delete archive</guimenuitem> creates a "
"subfolder in the folder with the archive, extracts the folders and files "
"into it and deletes the archive."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Raspakuj arhivu ovde, pogodi potfasciklu</guimenuitem> stvara "
"potfasciklu u fascikli u kojoj je arhiva, i u nju raspakuje fascikle i "
"fajlove iz arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>Extract Archive To...</guimenuitem> opens the Extract dialog "
#| "where you can choose destination folder and various extraction options."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract to…</guimenuitem> opens the Extract dialog where you "
"can choose the destination folder and various extraction options."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Raspakuj arhivu u...</guimenuitem> otvara dijalog raspakivanja, "
"gde možete izabrati odredišnu fasciklu i razne opcije raspakivanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin;'s context menu for a selection of files and/or folders displays "
"these actions in the <guimenu>Compress</guimenu> submenu:"
msgstr ""
"Pri aktivnom izboru, <application>Dolphinov</application> kontekstni meni "
"nad izabranim fajlovima i fasciklama daje sledeće radnje u podmeniju "
"<guimenu>Kompresuj</guimenu>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>Here (as TAR.GZ)</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Here (as "
#| "ZIP)</guimenuitem> creates these archive types in the current folder."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Compress to \"Archive.tar.gz\"</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Compress to \"Archive.zip\"</guimenuitem> creates these archive "
"types in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ovde (kao *.tar.gz)</guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem>Ovde (kao *."
"zip)</guimenuitem> stvaraju arhive ovih tipova u tekućoj fascikli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Compress to...</guimenuitem> opens a dialog where you can "
"select folder, name and archive type."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Kompresuj u...</guimenuitem> otvara dijalog u kojem možete "
"izabrati fasciklu, ime i tip arhive."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Batch Mode"
msgstr "Napredni paketni režim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; has an advanced batch mode to manage archives without launching a "
"graphical user interface. This mode allows you to extract or create archives "
"and add files to them."
msgstr ""
"<application>Ark</application> poseduje napredni paketni režim za rukovanje "
"arhivama bez pokretanja grafičkog sučelja. U ovom režimu možete raspakivati "
"i stvarati arhive, i dodavati fajlove u njih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The batch mode is documented in <ulink url=\"man:/ark\">&ark;'s man page</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Paketni režim dokumentuje <ulink url=\"man:/ark\">uputna stranica "
"<application>Arka</application></ulink>."

